---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="About Us - Attendance Tracker"
	description="Learn about the mission behind Attendance Tracker - the most advanced tool for students to manage their attendance and automate their bunking."
>
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-s-md py-s-4xl md:py-s-section">
		<h1 class="display-lg mb-s-xl tracking-tighter">About Attendance Tracker</h1>
		
		<div class="space-y-s-xl body-md text-body leading-relaxed">
			<p>
				Attendance Tracker was born out of a simple necessity: the need for a smarter, more intuitive way to manage college attendance. We understand that as a student, your time is precious, and keeping track of percentages shouldn't be a chore.
			</p>
			
			<h2 class="display-sm text-ink mt-s-2xl mb-s-md">Our Mission</h2>
			<p>
				Our mission is to empower students with data-driven insights into their academic schedule. We believe that by automating the "boring" parts of student life—like calculating how many classes you can skip—we can help you focus more on what actually matters.
			</p>

			<h2 class="display-sm text-ink mt-s-2xl mb-s-md">Built for Speed</h2>
			<p>
				Inspired by world-class developer tools like Vercel and Linear, we've built an interface that is fast, minimalist, and keyboard-centric. No clutter, no ads, just the data you need.
			</p>

			<div class="mt-s-3xl p-s-xl rounded-xl border border-hairline bg-canvas-soft shadow-level-1">
				<p class="body-sm italic">
					"We don't just track attendance; we predict your success and help you balance your student life effectively."
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
